== 1.3.0 (2013.08.05)

* Rails 4 support

== 1.2.2 (2013.03.08)

* Use rdoc/task instead of obsolete rake/rdoctask
* Fix compatibility with ActiveRecord 3.2.12

== 1.2.1 (2012.02.01)

* Remove use of ActiveSupport::Concern.
* Correct has_role? behavior after add_role on an invalid object.

== 1.2.0 (2011.01.27)

* Use class_attribute to provide Rails 3.1+ support.

== 1.1.3

* First stable version to support Rails 3.
